- start migrations for the different entities
- configure travis
- configure rspec to persist into RAKE_ENV['test']
- configure Rspec to destroy db after every test
- configure sinatra: RootApplication and all other inheriting from it (e.g. http://sinatrarb.com/configuration.html)
- configure sinatra to serve HTML views

- rake task to generate migration (e.g. DateTime.current.strftime('%Y%m%d%H%M%S')) 20080717013526_your_migration_name.rb
- explore railties gem for generating migrations, etc
